Package com.adobe.creativesdk.behance

Contains classes for interacting with Adobe Behance.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAdobeBehanceADDProjectModuleListener
    IAdobeBehanceADDProjectModuleListener is an interface for providing a callback for adding a project module.
    IAdobeBehanceCreateProjectDraftListener
    IAdobeBehanceCreateProjectDraftListener is an interface for providing a callback for saving a project draft.
    IAdobeBehanceGetCreativeFieldsListener
    Created by mayank on 22/9/16.
    IAdobeBehanceProjectPublishListener
    IAdobeBehanceProjectPublishListener is an interface for providing a callback for project publishing.
    IAdobeBehanceSDKEditProfileListener
    IAdobeBehanceSDKEditProfileListener is an interface for providing a callback for profile edits.
    IAdobeBehanceSDKGetUserProfileListener
    IAdobeBehanceSDKGetUserProfileListener is an interface for providing a callback retrieving a Behance user profile.
    IAdobeBehanceSDKPublishProjectResultIntentExtras
    IAdobeBehanceSDKPublishProjectResultIntentExtras is an interface for obtaining results from the Behance project publishing workflow.
    IAdobeBehanceSearchProjectListener
    IAdobeBehanceSearchProjectListener is an interface for providing a callback when a project search completes.
    IAdobeBehanceUpdateProfileListener
    IAdobeBehanceUpdateProfileListener is an interface for providing a callback when updating a profile.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdobeBehanceAddProjectWorkflowOptions
    Represents the workflow options for the creating a Behance Project.
    AdobeBehanceCustomizationOptions
    Represents the options to customize Behance publish Project notifications.
    AdobeBehanceEditProfileOptions
    Represents the options to edit Behance Profile.
    AdobeBehanceProjectDraftOptions
    Represents the options for the creating Behance Project Draft.
    AdobeBehanceSDKAbstractPublishOptions
    Represents options for publishing Behance Project and Work in Progress.
    AdobeBehanceSDKPublishProjectOptions
    Represents the options for the publishing Behance Project.
    AdobeBehanceSearchProjectOptions
    AdobeBehanceSearchProjectOptions represents the options for creating search query to search published Behance Projects.
    AdobeBehanceUpdateProfileOptions
    AdobeBehanceUpdateProfileOptions represents the options for the updating Behance user profile.
    AdobeUXBehanceWorkflow
    AdobeUXBehanceWorkflow has methods to publish Behance Project.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AdobeBehancePublishInvalidImageException
    Thrown to indicate the list of images passed to publish project contains an invalid image.
    BehanceSDKSecurityException
    Thrown to indicate security exception if the security manager check for permissions fails.

Package com.adobe.creativesdk.behance Description

Contains classes for interacting with Adobe Behance. Supports operations such as publishing a Behance project or work in progress.
